  "reference_number": "CAF0028",
  "remarks": "\nEvgeny Kopot is an involved person under the Central African Republic (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2020 as he is a member of, or associated with, the Wagner Group. The Wagner Group is or has been an involved person since it is or has engaged in a relevant activity namely the commission of violations of international humanitarian law in the Central African Republic, in particular the deliberate targeting of civilians. \n",
